    A Stackdriver Logging log entry. All log entries are represented via objects of this class. Log entries can have different type of payloads: an UTF-8 string (see Payload.StringPayload), a JSON object (see Payload.JsonPayload, or a protobuf object (see Payload.ProtoPayload). Entries can also store additional information about the operation or the HTTP request that generated the log (see operation() and httpRequest(), respectively).
